In order to print a page (and have it look nice) a user needs to click on the printer icon first.  This could be simplified by using a print style sheet reference on every page.  See this article:

http://www.alistapart.com/articles/goingtoprint/

This would load up a special style sheet only when a user is printing.  This would allow users to print any page without needed to go through the step of choosing the printer friendly page.
